OL,13,     Gthen climbs the Pennines.
OL,14,G0235FThe Normans
OL,15,     GProfessor Robert Bartlett
OL,16,     Gexplores the impact of the
OL,17,     GNormans on southern Europe and
OL,18,     Gthe Middle East, as they spread
OL,19,     Gsouth in the 11th century.
